snippet.title: Replay - The Legend Of Zelda: Majora's Mask
snippet.description: Join Game Informer's Andrew Reiner, Kyle Hilliard, Jeff Marchiafava, and Wade Wojcik as they revisit the Nintendo 64 classic ahead of upcoming planned re-release on 3DS.
